OL,3,CMan given three-year football ban
OL,4,Cafter punching 13-year-old after match
OL,6,FA man has been handed a three-year
OL,7,Ffootball ban after punching a 13-year-
OL,8,Fold in the face after a match.
OL,10,FSean Ryan, 21, assaulted the teenager
OL,11,Fas he walked past him following
OL,12,FSouthport FC's victory in the FA Cup
OL,13,Fsecond round qualifier against
OL,14,FRadcliffe FC in 2025.
OL,16,FHe was then detained by stadium staff.
