OL,3,CMan given three-year football ban
OL,4,Cafter punching 13-year-old after match
OL,6,FThe young victim - a Radcliffe
OL,7,Fsupporter - experienced soreness from
OL,8,Fthe assault and was left very
OL,9,Fdistressed by the unprovoked attack,
OL,10,FMerseyside Police said.
OL,12,FRyan, from Old Swan, Liverpool,
OL,13,Fpleaded guilty to common assault and
OL,14,Fwas issued the ban, alongside 120
OL,15,Fhours unpaid work, and ordered to pay
OL,16,F#250 compensation plus court costs at
OL,17,FSefton Magistrates Court on 15 January.
