OL,3,CMan given three-year football ban
OL,4,Cafter punching 13-year-old after match
OL,6,F"The young victim was left very
OL,7,Fdistressed after the incident and this
OL,8,Ftype of violent behaviour has no place
OL,9,Fin football," Inspector Stuart
OL,10,FMcLoughlin said.
OL,12,F"Thankfully Ryan quickly admitted the
OL,13,Fassault after it had happened, and now
OL,14,FRyan is banned from attending any
OL,15,Ffootball game in the country.
OL,17,F"Everyone should feel safe without any
OL,18,Ffear when they are attending a
OL,19,Ffootball game.
