OL,6,F"We will work to identify and bring to
OL,7,Fjustice anyone found responsible for
OL,8,Fcommitting any form of unacceptable
OL,9,Fand violent behaviour at football
OL,10,Fmatches.
OL,12,F"I hope this sends a clear message and
OL,13,Facts as a deterrent to others that we
OL,14,Fwill be put you before the courts to
OL,15,Fbe prosecuted."
